GnResponseDataMatches
GnResponseDataMatches Object Model
GnResponseDataMatches methods and child objects with brief descriptions:
[detail level 12345678910111213141516]
GnResponseDataMatchesCollection of data match results received in response to a data match query.
ResultCountResult count - number of matches returned
RangeStartRange start - ordinal value of first match in range total
RangeEndRange end - ordinal value of last match in range total
RangeTotalRange total - total number of matches that could be returned
NeedsDecisionFlag indicating if response needs user or app decision - either multiple matches returned or less than perfect single match
DataMatchesIterator for accessing response match(es).
GnDataMatchRepresents a match to query where any type of match is desired, album or contributor.
IsAlbumFlag indicating if match is album
IsContributorFlag indicating if match is contributor
GetAsAlbumIf album, get match as album object
GnAlbumCollection of audio recordings.
IsFullResultFlag indicating if response contains full (true) or partial (false) metadata.
